		<ul>
			<li>
				<a href="https://trinsic.id" target="blank">Trinsic</a>
				(feb 2023 – present): Founding engineer in the product team; identity
				verification software; iterating fast to find product market fit.
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="https://utahcounty.gov">Utah County Gov.</a>
				(aug 2022 – feb 2023): Web programmer in the information systems
				department.
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="https://pluralsight.com">Pluralsight</a> (summer 2022):
				Software engineering intern.
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="https://cs.byu.edu/"> BYU STaPL</a> (fall 2021 - winter
				2022): Research assistant in the Social Technologies and Privacy
				Lab (STaPL).
			</li>
		</ul>

